data.description: Welcome to 607 S Cowal Dr, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house nestled in the picturesque Texas Hill Country of Spicewood, TX. This beautiful home is perfect for investors, first-time homebuyers, and professionals seeking a serene and friendly community. Located in the highly sought-after Briarcliff Subdivision, this lovely home sits on a spacious .320-acre lot with ample room for outdoor living. The large front yard and fenced backyard are shaded by mature trees, providing a tranquil setting for relaxation and play. Just 1.5 miles from Briarcliff Boat Marina on Lake Travis, residents can enjoy fishing, swimming, and water recreation with ease. Inside, you'll find high ceilings, a cozy white stone fireplace, fresh interior and exterior paint, and new carpet in the spare bedrooms. The stainless steel appliances add a modern touch to the inviting kitchen. A large covered back patio is nestled among the oak trees, ready for entertaining family and friends in the heart of nature.
